dcterms:description: The dataset analyzes the affinity landscape spanned by the 15 point mutations separating the spike protein of the ancestral Wuhan strain of the SARS-CoV2 virus from the Omicron BA.1 variant.
dcterms:title: Affinity landscape of the SARS-CoV2 spike protein

dcterms:description: This dataset includes a fitness landscape comprising combinations of nucleotide mutations at 9 sites in the folA gene in Escherichia coli, revealing a landscape that combines high ruggedness with high accessibility.
dcterms:title: Fitness landscape of the dihydrofolate reductase (DHFR) enzyme in Escherichia coli
